item.title: Thank You Summer Interns
item.description: Many, many thanks to our departing undergraduate summer interns - Roxane Avalos, Ricardo Charcas, Juan Mancillas, Daniel Spalla, Taylor The, and Brandon Wolff. Your diligence and persistence in tracking down information about DCTT around the country this summer were critical to the project. We wish you all the best and look forward to collaborating with all of you in the future.
